# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Proxy list — one proxy per line, format: proto://user:pass@host:port
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used by the proxyloader service to rotate through proxies
# during upstream API fetches.
#
# Examples:
#   http://user:pass@proxy1.example.com:8080
#   socks5://user:pass@proxy2.example.com:1080
#   https://proxy3.example.com:443
#
# Copy this file to proxy.txt and populate with real proxies.
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
